        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/wintercodes-4k-2022-formula1/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/wintercodes-4k-2022-formula1/",
            "title": "Wintercodes 4K 2022 Formula1",
            "summary": "Ident made for Foxtel 4K UHD Wintercodes F1. I worked on designing the livery of the F1 car and also&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-meta\">\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711921077?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p class=\"\">Ident made for Foxtel 4K UHD Wintercodes F1. I worked on designing the livery of the F1 car and also did some additional detailing work on shots that Patrick Lloyd and Grischa Theissen had already done. <br><br>Art Directors: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/radge-ratsaphong-89094498/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Radge Ratsaphong</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tim-buhagiar-050b9a2b/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tim Buhagiar</a> <br>Design Director: <a href=\"https://www.sallyannekerr.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D Artists: Parag Satyal, <a href=\"http://grsh.me\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a>, Patrick Lloyd</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782027831577_109\" class=\"image-list\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782027831577_108\" class=\"image\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782027831577_116\" class=\"sqs-video-wrapper video-none\" data-load=\"false\" data-html=\"&lt;iframe allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture&quot; allowfullscreen src=&quot;https://player.vimeo.com/video/711921077?h=ce92825141&amp;amp;app_id=122963&amp;amp;wmode=opaque&quot; width=&quot;426&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; title=&quot;Foxtel_F1_15secIdent_4K.mp4&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\" data-provider-name=\"Vimeo\">\n<div class=\"intrinsic\">\n<div class=\"intrinsic-inner\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782027831577_1063\" class=\"sqs-video-overlay\">\n<div class=\"sqs-video-opaque\"> </div>\n<div class=\"sqs-video-icon\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Play\">\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/1.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/1-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-132641.png\" data-size=\"2717x1910\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-132641-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"540\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-133138-2.png\" data-size=\"3837x2077\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/39/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-133138-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"416\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
