        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/wintercodes-4k-2022-afl-ident/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/wintercodes-4k-2022-afl-ident/",
            "title": "Wintercodes 4K 2022 AFL Ident",
            "summary": "An ident made to promo Foxtel 4K UHD channel. The shoe was 3D scanned from an actual shoe and then&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711718499?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"project-meta\">\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<p class=\"\">An ident made to promo Foxtel 4K UHD channel. The shoe was 3D scanned from an actual shoe and then some additional texturing done in Substance Painter as the shoe needed to look used. All textures needed to made in 8K because the render was being done in 4K and 50 frames per second.<br><br>Art Directors: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/radge-ratsaphong-89094498/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Radge Ratsaphong</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tim-buhagiar-050b9a2b/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tim Buhagiar </a><br>Design Director: <a href=\"https://www.sallyannekerr.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D Artists: Parag Satyal and <a href=\"http://grsh.me\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a></p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/1-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/1-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/2-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/2-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/3-2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/3-2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-132444-2.png\" data-size=\"3835x2060\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/38/gallery/Screenshot-2022-05-20-132444-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"413\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
