        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/aande-idents-2/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/aande-idents-2/",
            "title": "A&amp;E Idents",
            "summary": "A series of Idents I made for A&amp;E to replace the their old ones. These were almost made as a&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/277749897?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_1.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_1-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_2.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_2-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_3.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/Weld_3-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>A series of Idents I made for A&amp;E to replace the their old ones. These were almost made as a passion project, whenever I had downtime. I used Substance Painter to texture and rendered using Arnold Renderer. I also used X-particles for particles and fluid sim.</p>\n<p>Design and 3D: Parag Satyal<br>Head of Design: <a href=\"https://www.michaelstrelan.com/about/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Michael Strelan</a><br>Sound Design: Simon Shipley</p>\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/277749692?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0100011.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0100011-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0200042.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0200042-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0300036.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/SHOT_0300036-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/260002609?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/a-e_fire_2_005500014.webp\" data-size=\"921x518\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/a-e_fire_2_005500014-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/a-e_fire_3_005500000.webp\" data-size=\"921x518\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/37/gallery/a-e_fire_3_005500000-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p> </p>\n</div>",
