        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sports-wintercodes-4k-2021/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sports-wintercodes-4k-2021/",
            "title": "Fox Sports Wintercodes 4K 2021",
            "summary": "This was made with a large team (for broadcast) and each of us worked on different shots. I worked on&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711601317?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p>This was made with a large team (for broadcast) and each of us worked on different shots. I worked on designing and building the CG interior set which had to match and seemlessly transition from the actual set. This was the first time I worked full ACES workflow for my shots.<br><br>Creative Director - <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave-sparx-94985419/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">David Sparkes</a><br>Design Director - <a href=\"https://www.sallyannekerr.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D - Parag Satyal, <a href=\"http://grsh.me\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a>, <a href=\"https://josephpole.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Joseph Pole</a><br>Compositing - Sally-Anne Kerr, <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/112994923\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Richard Grant</a>, <a href=\"http://www.tristanbrittaine.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tristan Brittaine</a><br>Grade - Tristan Brittaine<br>DOP - <a href=\"https://ashleighcarter.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ashleigh Carter</a></p>\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711606407?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/3.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/4.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/4-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/Snapshot.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/36/gallery/Snapshot-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
