        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sports-summer-of-cricket/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sports-summer-of-cricket/",
            "title": "Fox Sports Summer of Cricket",
            "summary": "This promo had a very tight deadline and the shots were distributed among several designers. My job was to work&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-meta\">\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711527564?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p class=\"\">This promo had a very tight deadline and the shots were distributed among several designers. My job was to work on warehouse shot. The brief was to make the warehouse look like a something that Wes Anderson would’ve designed. <br><br>Awards:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>2021 PromaxANZ Gold - Best Sports Promo</li>\n<li>2021 PromaxANZ Gold - Best Image Promo</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"\">Creative Director: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave-sparx-94985419/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">David Sparks</a><br>Design Director: <a href=\"https://www.sallyannekerr.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D Artists: Parag Satyal, <a href=\"http://grsh.me\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a><br>2D Artists: <a href=\"http://www.irongav.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gavin Tyrell</a>, <a href=\"https://m0rteza.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Morteza Shahbake</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782024276589_223\" class=\"image-list\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782024276589_222\" class=\"image\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782024276589_230\" class=\"sqs-video-wrapper video-none\" data-load=\"false\" data-html=\"&lt;iframe allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture&quot; allowfullscreen src=&quot;https://player.vimeo.com/video/711527564?h=75cbfb25e7&amp;amp;app_id=122963&amp;amp;wmode=opaque&quot; width=&quot;426&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; title=&quot;Summer of Cricket 2020&quot; height=&quot;240&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\" data-provider-name=\"Vimeo\">\n<div class=\"intrinsic\">\n<div class=\"intrinsic-inner\">\n<div id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1782024276589_1178\" class=\"sqs-video-overlay\">\n<div class=\"sqs-video-icon\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Play\">\n<figure class=\"post__video post__image\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711535158?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></figure>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/Snapshot.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" sizes=\"(min-width: 37.5em) 1600px, 80vw\" srcset=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/responsive/Snapshot-xs.jpg 384w ,https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/responsive/Snapshot-sm.jpg 600w ,https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/responsive/Snapshot-md.jpg 768w ,https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/responsive/Snapshot-lg.jpg 1200w ,https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/35/responsive/Snapshot-xl.jpg 1600w\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
