        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/mtv-summer-of-music-3/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/mtv-summer-of-music-3/",
            "title": "MTV Summer of Music",
            "summary": "For MTV Summer of Music we wanted to create a version of reality where everything is made of paper, raw&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/277836117?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p>For MTV Summer of Music we wanted to create a version of reality where everything is made of paper, raw cotton and foam. We got Benja Harney from Paperform to make all the props with paper. The spot has 3 different shots combined to make it look like a single shot, the birds were stop-motion animated using Benja's props and composited later. </p>\n<p>Concept and Art Direction: Parag Satyal<br>Creative Director: <a href=\"https://www.rasicandpartners.com\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vanessa Zuppicich</a><br>Props: <a href=\"https://studiopaperform.com/about/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Benja Harney</a><br>Direction: <a href=\"https://cargocollective.com/costavakas\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Costa Vakas</a><br>DOP: Adam Howden<br>Producer: Neil Bessant and Leah Harris<br>Set Design: Jamie Craney<br>Makeup: Deborah Munday</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/1.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/1-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/3.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/3-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/4.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/4-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/5.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/5-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/6.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/6-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/7.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/7-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/8.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/8-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\"><br>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/3.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"></a></figure>\n<br>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/34/gallery/5.webp\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
