        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/foxtel-express-release-2/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/foxtel-express-release-2/",
            "title": "Foxtel Express Release",
            "summary": "This was the first job I worked on remotely after we were forced to work from home when the pandemic&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711472461?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p>This was the first job I worked on remotely after we were forced to work from home when the pandemic hit in 2020. Everyone was scrambling to figure out a way to collaborate and quickly found the solution in Dropbox. I textured the helicopter in Substance Painter and built the last shot where the screen drops on the driveway. <br><br>Director: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefaniereinboth/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stephanie Reinboth</a><br>Design Director: <a href=\"https://www.paragsatyal.com/Design Director: Sally-Anne Kerr\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D Artist: <a href=\"http://grsh.me\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  >Grischa Theissen</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rakitha-vithanage-216a3b12/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rakitha Vithanage</a> and Parag Satyal</p>\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711512296?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/knickknack.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x1350\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/knickknack-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"960\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/Snapshot.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/Snapshot-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/Untitled-3.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/32/gallery/Untitled-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>",
