        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/selling-houses-australia-2/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/selling-houses-australia-2/",
            "title": "Selling Houses Australia",
            "summary": "Modelled, textured and lit a CGI house for a Selling Houses Australia promo on Lifestyle channel. The house needed to&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-meta\">\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/711463241?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\nModelled, textured and lit a CGI house for a Selling Houses Australia promo on Lifestyle channel. The house needed to look like it had a face and would need to show basic emotions. I also needed to design the house in three different states of disrepair for the story of the promo to make sense.<br><br>We went through several iterations of the house to find the one that looked very obviously like a face. One of the iteration of the houses got quite close to looking almost like a derelict haunted house which never made the cut but nevertheless is my favourite.<br><br>Awards:</div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"project-description\">Promax ANZ 2020 Best Entertainment Promo - Gold</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"project-description\"><br>Creative Director: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mikki-katz-60076b38/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mikki Katz</a><br>Promo Producer and Director: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefaniereinboth/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Stephanie Reinboth</a><br>3D Artist: Parag Satyal<br>Additional 3D: <a href=\"http://grsh.me\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a><br>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92041644_768833633644668_5507140111192901526_n.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x610\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92041644_768833633644668_5507140111192901526_n-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"434\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92206608_1891803087618790_5686690471031443633_n.jpg\" data-size=\"870x489\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92206608_1891803087618790_5686690471031443633_n-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92348926_531738090869424_5836561650176268114_n.jpg\" data-size=\"1080x611\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92348926_531738090869424_5836561650176268114_n-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"434\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92374512_558748985058459_5185720194047539737_n.jpg\" data-size=\"888x499\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92374512_558748985058459_5185720194047539737_n-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92395927_678881079552166_726723062717175910_n.jpg\" data-size=\"881x495\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/31/gallery/92395927_678881079552166_726723062717175910_n-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
