        {
            "id": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sleuth-ident-2/",
            "url": "https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/fox-sleuth-ident-2/",
            "title": "Fox Sleuth Ident",
            "summary": "The ident is meant to represent a common thread among the channel's three flagship characters: Hercule Poirot, Miss Marple and&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-meta\">\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<figure class=\"post__video\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/396872294?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=8dc7dc&dnt=1\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></figure>\n<p class=\"\">The ident is meant to represent a common thread among the channel's three flagship characters: Hercule Poirot, Miss Marple and Jessica Fletcher. Each scene is meant to represent each of the characters in form of their work space, where they do all their work.</p>\n<p class=\"\">I worked on Miss Marple ,Jessica Fletcher and the door scenes. All assets were textured using Substance Painter.<br><br>Creative Director: <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/authwall?sessionRedirect=https%3A%2F%2Fau.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmikki-katz-60076b38\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mikki Katz</a><br>Design Director: <a href=\"https://www.sallyannekerr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sally-Anne Kerr</a><br>3D Artists: <a href=\"https://grsh.me/\" target=\"_blank\"  class=\"extlink extlink-icon-1\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grischa Theissen</a> and Parag Satyal</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"4\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/FOXSLEUTH_IdentDetective_Blocking_ForCollection_IdentDetective_Blocking_05_2022-05-18_15.20.49.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/FOXSLEUTH_IdentDetective_Blocking_ForCollection_IdentDetective_Blocking_05_2022-05-18_15.20.49-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/FOXSLEUTH_IdentDetective_Blocking_ForCollection_IdentDetective_Blocking_05_2022-05-18_19.55.42.png\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/FOXSLEUTH_IdentDetective_Blocking_ForCollection_IdentDetective_Blocking_05_2022-05-18_19.55.42-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Glasses.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Glasses-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/MissMarple_Book_MASTER.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/MissMarple_Book_MASTER-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/MissMarple_Map_Book_01.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/MissMarple_Map_Book_01-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Sofa2.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Sofa2-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Teacup_02.jpg\" data-size=\"1920x1080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://paragsatyal.github.io/portfolio/media/posts/30/gallery/Teacup_02-thumbn